Class ElasticSearchRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.drivr.ElasticSearchRequest

  • public class ElasticSearchRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to hold the document gotten for requests in ElasticSearch before converting it to a proper request.
